                            <comment id="14207895" author="yaytay" created="Wed, 12 Nov 2014 10:14:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The workaround is to repackage your interceptors using a &lt;a href=&quot;http://cxf.apache.org/docs/features.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CXF Feature&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
You can see from the code excerpted from BusDefinitionParser.java that features don&apos;t use a getter and thus avoid the problem.&lt;br/&gt;
Irritating then, but not a complete blocker.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
